{"title":"钢花赞（外一首）","authors":["绥民"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":1,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢花赞（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绥民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金色的钢花飞舞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"布满了整个车间；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千朵万朵万万朵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火红，晶莹，耀眼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炼钢工人的理想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟钢花一样灿烂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正在满天作飞旋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"编织幸福的图案。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一幅画金光闪闪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就在图案中出现："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿野，晴空，蓝天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝天下工厂，田园；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千万支巨大的烟囱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像钢铁工人巨掌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把祖国高高举起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，一片辉煌灿烂……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“驯狮”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"转炉像一头雄狮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抖着金色的鬃毛；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它大声吼着晃着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喷吐出金光万道。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们驯狮的英雄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在炉前眯着眼瞧："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他紧紧掌住摇手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫它低头，抬头，笑！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一挥手天车驰来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送来圆圆的钢包；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哨声起转炉俯首，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吐三吨，一点不敢少！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"密密的钢花飞溅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车间里轻霞照耀；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄们挥一把汗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又熔炼幸福金涛……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}